00:41:07,399 --> 00:41:08,965
¶ I'm the one ¶

1039
00:41:08,967 --> 00:41:11,601
¶ I'm the one and only one. ¶

1040
00:41:27,385 --> 00:41:30,019
You were right.

1041
00:41:30,021 --> 00:41:32,522
You are nothing like Father.

1042
00:41:32,524 --> 00:41:36,159
Oh? What changed
                      your mind?

1043
00:41:36,161 --> 00:41:37,994
If I tell you this,
                you have to come

1044
00:41:37,996 --> 00:41:39,529
completely clean
                with me, Mother.

1045
00:41:39,531 --> 00:41:43,032
No more secrets, Mom.
No more lies.

1046
00:41:45,303 --> 00:41:47,203
Okay.

1047
00:41:48,540 --> 00:41:50,240
What happened?

1048
00:41:50,242 --> 00:41:54,043
35 years ago, Father,

1049
00:41:54,045 --> 00:41:55,245
He asked me
to come down here

1050
00:41:55,247 --> 00:41:57,447
to bless a couple who was
unable to have a child.

1051
00:41:57,449 --> 00:41:59,916
He had never asked me
to do anything of this sort,

1052
00:41:59,918 --> 00:42:02,485
and He never did again.

1053
00:42:02,487 --> 00:42:03,720
Today...

1054
00:42:05,357 --> 00:42:07,290
I met the mother again.

1055
00:42:09,327 --> 00:42:11,361
And I found out what the result

1056
00:42:11,363 --> 00:42:13,162
of that miracle was.

1057
00:42:15,066 --> 00:42:16,666
Or, rather, who.

1058
00:42:16,668 --> 00:42:18,568
(elevator bell dings)

1059
00:42:19,638 --> 00:42:22,038
Oh, hey.
                      Detective.

1060
00:42:22,040 --> 00:42:24,207
Sorry, I thought...
        What are you doing here?

1061
00:42:24,209 --> 00:42:25,942
Are you on your way out?

1062
00:42:25,944 --> 00:42:27,577
I am, yes.

1063
00:42:27,579 --> 00:42:29,078
Oh...
           To see you, actually.

1064
00:42:29,080 --> 00:42:31,347
Oh.

1065
00:42:31,349 --> 00:42:34,484
I believe I owe you dinner.

1066
00:42:34,486 --> 00:42:38,621
MOM:
        <i> Now we know why</i>
      <i> Chloe's so special.</i>

1067
00:42:38,623 --> 00:42:41,291
Don't we?

1068
00:42:41,293 --> 00:42:43,626
Your Father put her here.

1069
00:42:43,628 --> 00:42:45,595
In Lucifer's path.

1070
00:42:47,666 --> 00:42:49,299
You know what this means?

1071
00:42:49,301 --> 00:42:53,369
It means...
       that I was a pawn.

1072
00:42:53,371 --> 00:42:56,739
¶ Can you feel it
  coming in the air tonight ¶

1073
00:42:56,741 --> 00:42:58,007
Say when.

1074
00:42:58,009 --> 00:42:59,242
When!
           (laughter)

1075
00:42:59,244 --> 00:43:00,710
When.

1076
00:43:00,712 --> 00:43:02,245
I hope you know
it takes months

1077
00:43:02,247 --> 00:43:03,379
to get a reservation
at this place.

1078
00:43:03,381 --> 00:43:05,515
Oh, yeah.
          The fries are amazing.

1079
00:43:05,517 --> 00:43:07,383
Oh, thank you.
I made them myself.

1080
00:43:10,655 --> 00:43:12,488
It means Chloe's
                not an obstacle.

1081
00:43:12,490 --> 00:43:15,525
She's how you'll
            get your wings back.

1082
00:43:15,527 --> 00:43:18,528
She's how we'll
               get it all back.

1083
00:43:18,530 --> 00:43:21,130
¶ But I don't know
        if you know... ¶

1084
00:43:21,132 --> 00:43:23,666
Detective?

1085
00:43:23,668 --> 00:43:27,337
What you said
today in the courtroom...

1086
00:43:27,339 --> 00:43:29,072
It was the truth.

1087
00:43:29,074 --> 00:43:32,375
¶ In the air tonight ¶

1088
00:43:32,377 --> 00:43:34,210
¶ Oh, Lord ¶

1089
00:43:35,547 --> 00:43:38,648
¶ I've been waiting
       for this moment ¶

1090
00:43:38,650 --> 00:43:41,517
We're going home, son.

1091
00:43:41,519 --> 00:43:45,555
And Chloe is the Key.

1092
00:43:45,557 --> 00:43:48,791
¶ I can feel it coming ¶

1093
00:43:48,793 --> 00:43:52,462
¶ In the air tonight ¶

1094
00:43:52,464 --> 00:43:53,696
¶ Oh, Lord. ¶

